Description: Epiphone Les Paul Classic Quilt TopNo longer available for purchase but you can read more about it and see reviews on musicians friend website:https://www.musiciansfriend.com/guitars/epiphone-les-paul-classic-quilt-top Included:-Gibson 490T Pickup Installed - https://store.gibson.com/products/490t-modern-classic-bridge-pickup/ - $129 retail-Gibson 490R Pickup Installed - https://store.gibson.com/products/490r-modern-classic-neck-pickup/ - $119 retail-Les Paul friendly hard shell case-Spare strap :) Please read below regarding current state of guitar: Guitar is in good shape but has obvious normal wear from play. Some scuffs and minor scratches. No big damage on body. See pictures for quality. I upgraded the pickups from the stock to Gibson 490R/T combo which sounds great and prevented me from buying a real LP! This hasn't been played in a while. I am removing the strings before sale. It will need a setup. The pickup selector knob is missing. A friend installed the pickups backwards. The pickup selector knob selects the opposite pickup from the label but still works fine. Something I just got used to since I didn't have the tools to fix it. The volume/tone knobs are all wired correctly and work as expected. Still plays well and sounds great. If you have any questions or want more pictures just let me know! Thanks for looking.
Title: Epiphone Les Paul Classic, Red Quilt Top, w/ Custom Gibson 490R/T pickup combo
